                        <h1><a name="11451"></a><a href="/blogs/readMore.html?id=11451">Work, Work and more Work</a></h1>
                        <div class="ItemInfo">[<a href="/blogs/selectBlog.html?id=2733&amp;articleId=11451" alt="Use this to refer to the specific blog entry">URL</a>] Posted on 10 June 2004 17:44,  <a href="/blogs/readMore.html?id=11451">0 comments in 0 threads.</a> Last comment on 10 June 2004 17:44.
                        </div>
                        <div>Sometimes real life gets in the way. With a blatant disregard to one's wishes for some peace and quiet, thus allowing the
                           pursuit of another line of business (which just happens to be a hobby as well), the creature called the "paying job" just
                           keeps intruding.
                           
                           <p>The short of it is, I haven't had much time in the last day or so to post here. And that's not likely to change for another
                              day or two, so please accept my apologies in advance. As they say in television-land, "Normal reception will resume as soon
                              as possible." Oh well, at least I managed to sneak some feedback to Richard on the Shard he's working on! *evil grin* Yes,
                              it's true, I am indeed a picky blighter. It's the voices in my head, you know, the ones that whisper to me at night and tell
                              me to...
                           </p>
                           
                           <p>Take kaer, J;)</p>
                        </div><br></td>
